title: All Blacks recall McCaw, drop Naholo for RWC quarterfinals
text: All Blacks recall McCaw, drop Naholo for RWC quarterfinals Thursday, 15 October 2015 (2 minutes ago) SWANSEA, Wales (AP) " New Zealand recalled captain Richie McCaw after an injury and dropped winger Waisake Naholo for the Rugby World Cup quarterfinal against France in Cardiff on Saturday.Julian Savea and Nehe Milner-Skudder were...
